@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam classBorderColor #F57F17
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Shipped : approve
Shipped --> Archived : process
Archived --> Reviewed : cancel
Archived : entry / log book
Reviewed --> Active : confirm
Reviewed : entry / log book
Active --> Closed : cancel
Pending --> Reviewed : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml